s_TED_Salon_-_Image_2.jpeg?w=1024&h=549&q=85 1024w","srcWebp":"//images.ctfassets.net/2h1qowfuxkq7/72E0uWH4X64Wsm6p2DKcGm/4a2212826043943b7d50b626bab45348/Doha_Debates_TED_Salon_-_Image_2.jpeg?w=1120&h=600&q=85&fm=webp","srcSetWebp":"//images.ctfassets.net/2h1qowfuxkq7/72E0uWH4X64Wsm6p2DKcGm/4a2212826043943b7d50b626bab45348/Doha_Debates_TED_Salon_-_Image_2.jpeg?w=280&h=150&q=85&fm=webp 280w,\n//images.ctfassets.net/2h1qowfuxkq7/72E0uWH4X64Wsm6p2DKcGm/4a2212826043943b7d50b626bab45348/Doha_Debates_TED_Salon_-_Image_2.jpeg?w=560&h=300&q=85&fm=webp 560w,\n//images.ctfassets.net/2h1qowfuxkq7/72E0uWH4X64Wsm6p2DKcGm/4a2212826043943b7d50b626bab45348/Doha_Debates_TED_Salon_-_Image_2.jpeg?w=1024&h=549&q=85&fm=webp 1024w","sizes":"(max-width: 1120px) 100vw, 1120px"},"singleMode":{"aspectRatio":1.7906976744186047,"src":"//images.ctfassets.net/2h1qowfuxkq7/72E0uWH4X64Wsm6p2DKcGm/4a2212826043943b7d50b626bab45348/Doha_Debates_TED_Salon_-_Image_2.jpeg?w=1540&h=860&q=85&fit=pad","srcSet":"//images.ctfassets.net/2h1qowfuxkq7/72E0uWH4X64Wsm6p2DKcGm/4a2212826043943b7d50b626bab45348/Doha_Debates_TED_Salon_-_Image_2.jpeg?w=385&h=215&q=85&fit=pad 385w,\n//images.ctfassets.net/2h1qowfuxkq7/72E0uWH4X64Wsm6p2DKcGm/4a2212826043943b7d50b626bab45348/Doha_Debates_TED_Salon_-_Image_2.jpeg?w=770&h=430&q=85&fit=pad 770w,\n//images.ctfassets.net/2h1qowfuxkq7/72E0uWH4X64Wsm6p2DKcGm/4a2212826043943b7d50b626bab45348/Doha_Debates_TED_Salon_-_Image_2.jpeg?w=1024&h=572&q=85&fit=pad 1024w","srcWebp":"//images.ctfassets.net/2h1qowfuxkq7/72E0uWH4X64Wsm6p2DKcGm/4a2212826043943b7d50b626bab45348/Doha_Debates_TED_Salon_-_Image_2.jpeg?w=1540&h=860&q=85&fm=webp&fit=pad","srcSetWebp":"//images.ctfassets.net/2h1qowfuxkq7/72E0uWH4X64Wsm6p2DKcGm/4a2212826043943b7d50b626bab45348/Doha_Debates_TED_Salon_-_Image_2.jpeg?w=385&h=215&q=85&fm=webp&fit=pad 385w,\n//images.ctfassets.net/2h1qowfuxkq7/72E0uWH4X64Wsm6p2DKcGm/4a2212826043943b7d50b626bab45348/Doha_Debates_TED_Salon_-_Image_2.jpeg?w=770&h=430&q=85&fm=webp&fit=pad 770w,\n//images.ctfassets.net/2h1qowfuxkq7/72E0uWH4X64Wsm6p2DKcGm/4a2212826043943b7d50b626bab45348/Doha_Debates_TED_Salon_-_Image_2.jpeg?w=1024&h=572&q=85&fm=webp&fit=pad 1024w","sizes":"(max-width: 1540px) 100vw, 1540px"}}}]},{"__typename":"ContentfulModuleBodyText","id":"58850ae9-41d7-5c51-9da8-2988fa67dd01","text":{"childMarkdownRemark":{"html":"<p>Through the Portals, the audience in New York heard about how the news media has shaped students’ lives in Doha, and how social media and technology are a crucial opportunity for women in Afghanistan, hearing first-hand from participants in Herat. Students in Mexico City highlighted the need to work across differences after elections in Mexico, while students from West Virginia, in the US, discussed resistance to change in their community. Meanwhile, Rwandans in Kigali also shared thoughts about how the trade war between Rwanda and the US affects them. </p>\n<p>TED and Doha Debates are building bridges and conversations in settings where differences are heard, assumptions are questioned, and views are openly and thoughtfully challenged. Doha Debates’ and Shared<em>Studio’s Doha</em>Portal is now available to visit at Qatar National Library.</p>"}}}]}]}},"pageContext":{"id":"6b8nf9LvglvT4CAGVm8jxS","languageCode":"en-US","alternateLanguage":"/ar/media-center/doha-debates-hosts-ted-salon-'up-for-debate'-in-partnership-with-ted-and","currSlug":"/media-center/doha-debates-hosts-ted-salon-'up-for-debate'-in-partnership-with-ted-and","title":"Doha Debates Hosts Ted Salon ‘Up For Debate’ in Partnership  With TED and Shared_Studios"}}}